<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="messy-adj">messy <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mesi/    美 /'mesi/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>凌乱的；肮脏的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a messy bookshelf 
凌乱的书架</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The room was always messy.
这个房间总是乱糟糟的。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>棘手的；难办的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Quite a difficult and messy task! 
真是相当棘手的任务！</p><footer>人教⑧ – 5</footer></div></div>